feat: Enhance settings and update specification

This commit introduces several improvements to the settings functionality and updates the specification document.

- **Settings:**
  - Added the ability to export and import settings to/from a JSON file.
  - Added a "Restore Defaults" button to reset all settings to their initial values.
- **Documentation:**
  - Updated `doc/SPECIFICATION.md` to accurately reflect the current feature set and future extension plans.
  - Restructured the document for better readability.